    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking for a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been super reliable and is in wonderful shape, perfect for someone who wants a solid, well-loved car without the 'new car' price tag. It drives like a dream and has plenty of life left in it! Come say hi and take it for a spin\u2014I'm sure you're going to love it as much as I have! \u2728",
      "price": 31500.0,
