      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "For sale is a driver-focused BMW E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six. This example delivers sharp throttle response via its factory individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. Essential preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure longitudinal rigidity. The suspension has been upgraded with Bilstein dampers for improved transient response and cornering stability. While the exterior shows minor patina consistent with a well-loved enthusiast vehicle, the mechanical vitals are robust, with the limited-slip differential providing consistent lock-up and predictable exit traction. A purist\u2019s machine ready for the canyons.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean interior. Runs well. Clean title.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2017 BMW 340i finished in Mineral Grey Metallic. This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of luxury and performance. The exterior paint retains a deep, lustrous shine, though there are a few minor stone chips on the front hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel consistent with careful daily use. The interior is smoke-free and features Oyster Dakota leather that remains soft and supportive, with only very light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every feature, from the heated seats to the premium Harman Kardon audio system and the sunroof, operates exactly as intended. Under the hood, the turbocharged B58 engine runs flawlessly with no leaks, weird noises, or hesitation. I have followed a proactive maintenance schedule, including oil changes every 5,000 miles. Within the last 3,000 miles, I have installed a fresh set of Michelin Pilot Sport tires and replaced the front brake rotors and pads. The car tracks straight, shifts smoothly through all eight gears, and provides a tight, responsive driving experience. It comes with a complete set of records, two key fobs, and the original floor mats. This is a reliable, high-performance sedan that has been treated with respect and is ready for its next home.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptionally well-maintained vehicle, offering a premier driving experience for the sophisticated professional. Characterized by its robust mechanical history and a refined aesthetic presence, this automobile demonstrates a commitment to quality and consistent care. It features a host of premium amenities and has undergone a rigorous inspection to ensure it meets our exacting standards for performance and reliability. This is a definitive selection for those seeking a balance of luxury and proven longevity.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by! I\u2019m parting ways with my reliable ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a gem. It\u2019s in really solid condition and has plenty of life left for its next owner. Whether you're heading to work or hitting the road for a trip, this car is ready to go! I\u2019ve taken good care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019re going to love how it drives. I\u2019m looking for a smooth, easy sale, so feel free to reach out if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 28900.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sorted BMW E46 M3, a quintessential driver\u2019s machine. At its heart is the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure VANOS system that has been recently serviced for precise variable valve timing. Power is managed via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a functional M-Variable differential lock. The chassis is reinforced at the rear subframe mounting points, addressing the platform's known fatigue areas. Suspension remains tight with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers. While the exterior shows minor stone chips and road patina, the drivetrain exhibits excellent compression and linear power delivery. This is a robust, performance-ready example for the purist.",
      "price": 34500.0,
